{"tid":1027819,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"任正非：世界離不開華為　絕不當中國政府間諜　或縮小公司規模","createTime":"2019-02-19T05:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T00:11:24.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"0f9bf860f9dab033a2f9b8874a8a1d80cc07ee91","tid":1027819,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:15:40.000Z","msg":"任正非：世界離不開華為 絕不當中國政府間諜 或縮小公司規模<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/%E4%BB%BB%E6%AD%A3%E9%9D%9E-%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%8D%E9%96%8B%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA-%E7%B5%95%E4%B8%8D%E7%95%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C-%E6%88%96%E7%B8%AE%E5%B0%8F%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1/?fbclid=IwAR0dLXyMWNKoAl-hBD8d5Z1q6g1uEXmQi3voVwOF4dmtTrJy04E_0cmHxK0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E9%259D%259E-%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E9%259B%25A2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E7%25B5%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%2595%25B6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25AB%259C-%25E6%2588%2596%25E7%25B8%25AE%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E8%25A6%258F%25E6%25A8%25A1%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0dLXyMWNKoAl-hBD8d5Z1q6g1uEXmQi3voVwOF4dmtTrJy04E_0cmHxK0&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEsljX8qB7Opg6os1DAz3scM%3D&h=42bbd7af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E9%259D%259E-%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E9%259B%25A2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E7%25B5%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%2595%25B6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25AB%259C-%25E6%2588%2596%25E7%25B8%25AE%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E8%25A6%258F%25E6%25A8%25A1%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0dLXyMWNKoAl-hBD8d5Z1q6g1uEXmQi3voVwOF4dmtTrJy04E_0cmHxK0&h=98f5e58a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/%E4%BB%BB%E6%AD%A3%E9%9D%9E-%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%8D%E9%96%8B%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA-%E7%B5%95%E4%B8%8D%E7%95%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C-%E6%88%96%E7%B8%AE%E5%B0%8F%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1/?fbclid=IwAR0dLXyMWNKoAl-hBD8d5Z1q6g1uEXmQi3voVwOF4dmtTrJy04E_0cmHxK0</a><br />\n<br />\n近月被西方國家圍堵的中國電訊設備巨頭華為，其創辦人任正非接受英國 BBC 專訪時再次強調，華為決不會充當中國政府的間諜。任正非表示，中國政府沒有要求華為這麼做，華為也不會這麼做，對於華為這樣一個超級大公司，不值得冒這樣的風險。<br />\n<br />\n任正非說：「我們永遠不會接受任何人要求華為設『後門』的指令，如果我們有任何這樣的行為，我本人會關閉公司」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>或縮小公司規模</strong><br />\n<br />\n他又指其女兒、華為首席財務官孟晚舟被捕是出於政治動機，是不可接受的。又指美國動不動就會用制裁手段，但既然事已至此，唯有交由法庭去處理。<br />\n<br />\n任正非又相信，即使面對美國圍堵，華為都不會被擊潰，「世界離不開我們，因為我們擁有更先進的技術。就算美國說服更多國家暫時不要使用我們的產品，我們總是能略為縮小規模。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>擴大投資英國</strong><br />\n<br />\n對於英國可能禁用華為產品，任正非稱這不會導致該公司撤回英國投資，並稱若美國持續采取行動抵制華為產品，將把在美國的投資轉移至英國，我們將擴大在英國的投資。因為美國若不信任我們，我們將會更大規模地把美國的投資轉到英國。」"},{"pid":"f99ce450268b59dcb1a74d7c6bfd83e9b3453f9a","tid":1027819,"uid":41035,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:22:42.000Z","msg":"一早有準備<br />\n就係等你講唔幫中國開後門做間諜先<br />\n之後先釘死你"},{"pid":"88971044fbf609655c4a52b50383bccd0cde469c","tid":1027819,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b1915b1f4dbec9e75847712e5485e605e5fffa","tid":1027819,"uid":12904,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:26:29.000Z","msg":"唔接受任何人，但接受黨"},{"pid":"1322b6dbcedaf4933a529e571aec110024fd7d13","tid":1027819,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呵呵呵"},{"pid":"00ea72b9c9e72a8d52852864ba980bbf5fb350ef","tid":1027819,"uid":16676,"like":3,"dislike":2,"scor